::: notes
We also coded for the specific area of law AND reference to legal doctrine including: reference to case law, reference to statute(s), reference to state or federal constitutional amendment(s), and reference to specific policy. The later 4 variables were coded for level of analysis -- we had 3 levels -- (1) no mention, (2) but only mentions, such as in the literature review, and (3) deeper legal analysis.
:::

